Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.39,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm's acting up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,So logically you got out of bed, dressed yourself completely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:18.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,and decided to gaze menacingly out into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:23.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I've trusted him for years, we both have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I just..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:29.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel..like he's keeping us in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.04,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.45,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You know very well that we are not the ones in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.41,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it worse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:40.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe that a man I've trusted for so long..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:41.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,would act so..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:42.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,passively
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.76,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person, James
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always done what you think is best for the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:51.26,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Even against strong protest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's admirable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:58.32,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's high time you stopped talking about trust and started showing it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:02.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozpin has experience that the rest of us lack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think that's something worth remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.49,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Blake, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:50.89,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:54.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think he asked us about being a Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.63,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Like..what was he trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.13,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was just curious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.34,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.66,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm awake! You two are talking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.98,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think he..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:15.51,D,,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I wanted to honor my family's name, I meant it, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.55,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:22.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stupid, I'm fully aware of what my father has done with the Schnee Dust Company
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he took control, our business has operated in a..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.39,D,,0000,0000,0000,,moral grey area
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's putting it lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I feel the needs to make things right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:36.52,D,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd taken a job in Atlas, it wouldn't have changed anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:42.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was not the start of our name, and I refuse to let him be the end of it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:46.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,All my life, I fought for what I thought was right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.85,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a partner named Adam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,More of a mentor, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,He always assured me that what we were doing would make the world a better place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.84,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, his idea of a perfect future turned out to be..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.76,D,,0000,0000,0000,,not perfect for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.57,D,,0000,0000,0000,,because I knew Huntsmen and Huntresses were regarded as the most noble warriors in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:10.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Always fighting for good
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.77,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never really thought past that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.14,D,,0000,0000,0000,,When I leave the Academy..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.28,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.10,D,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I undo so many years of hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.35,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd figure it out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:24.48,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to back down from a challenge, Blake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.48,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:31.32,D,,0000,0000,0000,,When you learned I was a Faunus, I didn't know what to do, so I ran
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized my oldest partner had become a monster, I ran
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.29,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my Semblance..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born with the ability to leave behind a shadow of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:44.37,D,,0000,0000,0000,,an empty copy that takes the hit while I run away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.84,D,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you two have something that drives you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just kinda of always, gone with the flow, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.91,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's fine, I mean, that's who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.92,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But how long can I really do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.35,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be a Huntress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,not really because I wanna be a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.14,D,,0000,0000,0000,,but because I want the adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.59,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a life where I won't know what tomorrow will bring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.54,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And that'll be a good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a Huntress just happens to line up with that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.73,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like Ruby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.86,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always wanted to be a Huntress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she said
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she was a kid, she'd judged about being the heroes in the books
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:27.41,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping people and saving the day, and never asking for anything else in return
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:31.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she couldn't fight, she knew that's what she wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.92,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she trained so hard to get where she is today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.16,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's still just a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only two years younger, we're all kids
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.23,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look where we are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.82,D,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of a warzone and armed to the teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.33,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the life we chose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a job
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:56.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We all had this romanticized vision of being a Huntress in our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the end of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.71,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a job to protect the people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:04.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And whatever we want, will have to come seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.16,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah -v-?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:20.10,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei, it's late, go back to bed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.23,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei, Zwei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.21,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.00,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:43.02,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.72,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.88,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei, this is a wasteland, you literally could've done that anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a Beowolf or something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:03.20,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ughn, let's just finish our patrol and get back to base
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.46,D,,0000,0000,0000,,This place gives me the creeps
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they go in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.94,D,,0000,0000,0000,,One bark means yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.41,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is it, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we gotta get the others
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.62,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.78,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:28.03,D,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a long way from home, little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.83,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.17,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss is gonna want to see this one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.65,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Weiss, it's your..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.42,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.83,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.83,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.07,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab your weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.94,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leader may be in trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand, I can't fix it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.51,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:26.48,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do, blow us to the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.79,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.18,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.29,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Found something you might wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:39.33,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good or bad, Perry, because let me tell you, I have had a day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's a little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.27,D,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be bad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby's scythe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.56,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.68,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.78,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Down there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.25,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.15,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:02.19,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, of course, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:02.95,D,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.35,D,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.36,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Oobleck, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain Glenn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.43,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, an expansion of Vale that was inevitably destroyed by creatures of Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously home to thousands of people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Working people commuting to the city, the main city
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.24,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Developed a subway system to the inner city
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.94,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimm attacks increased, population endangered, now desperately searching for shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.64,D,,0000,0000,0000,,City evacuates into the metro tunnels and what did they find?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:27.50,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The southeast quadrant of Vale is known for wild forests and deep caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.42,D,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear, we're not just looking for an underground crime network
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.98,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for an 'underground' crime network!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.32,D,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been working in caves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.38,D,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, Mountain Glenn was Vale's first serious attempt at expansion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:42.30,D,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked for a short period of time, thanks to an aggressive perimeter defense
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.40,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And unique transportation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.12,D,,0000,0000,0000,,The city developed an elaborate subway system
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.14,D,,0000,0000,0000,,to carry citizens safely from the new territory into the main Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.06,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, without the many natural barriers Vale had to protect its borders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.07,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain Glenn was doomed from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:58.34,D,,0000,0000,0000,,As the end drew near, the citizens of the territory made one last attempt to survival
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.22,D,,0000,0000,0000,,They took up shelter beneath the city
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.76,D,,0000,0000,0000,,In massive caves that they had cleared out for the subway
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.16,D,,0000,0000,0000,,And they had cut themselves off from the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,An underground village?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.80,D,,0000,0000,0000,,In a matter of speaking, yes, a safe haven
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.49,D,,0000,0000,0000,,Until..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.96,D,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion opened the mouth of another cavern
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.53,D,,0000,0000,0000,,filled with subterranean Grimm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.60,D,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the Kingdom officially sealed off the tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.67,D,,0000,0000,0000,,creating the world's largest tomb
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.08,D,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ruby is down there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.45,D,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find her
